name: $sequence
desc: Returns: A number to uniquely identify item entries.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: A number to uniquely identify item entries.

name: $revenue
desc: Returns: The type of revenue or cost center providing the product and/or service.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The type of revenue or cost center providing the product and/or service.

name: $category
desc: Returns: Code to identify the general type of benefits under which products and services are provided.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Code to identify the general type of benefits under which products and services are provided.

name: $productOrService
desc: Returns: When the value is a group code then this item collects a set of related claim details, otherwise this contains the product, service, drug or other billing code for the item.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: When the value is a group code then this item collects a set of related claim details, otherwise this contains the product, service, drug or other billing code for the item.

name: $modifier
desc: Returns: Item typification or modifiers codes to convey additional context for the product or service.

name: $addmodifier
desc: Item typification or modifiers codes to convey additional context for the product or service.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: Item typification or modifiers codes to convey additional context for the product or service.

name: $programCode
desc: Returns: Identifies the program under which this may be recovered.

name: $addprogramCode
desc: Identifies the program under which this may be recovered.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: Identifies the program under which this may be recovered.

name: $quantity
desc: Returns: The number of repetitions of a service or product.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The number of repetitions of a service or product.

name: $unitPrice
desc: Returns: If the item is not a group then this is the fee for the product or service, otherwise this is the total of the fees for the details of the group.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: If the item is not a group then this is the fee for the product or service, otherwise this is the total of the fees for the details of the group.

name: $factor
desc: Returns: A real number that represents a multiplier used in determining the overall value of services delivered and/or goods received. The concept of a Factor allows for a discount or surcharge multiplier to be applied to a monetary amount.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: A real number that represents a multiplier used in determining the overall value of services delivered and/or goods received. The concept of a Factor allows for a discount or surcharge multiplier to be applied to a monetary amount.

name: $net
desc: Returns: The quantity times the unit price for an additional service or product or charge.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The quantity times the unit price for an additional service or product or charge.

name: $udi
desc: Returns: Unique Device Identifiers associated with this line item.
